[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 0.7,
    "text": "Hi, I'm Chris Evans."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 0.7,
    "endTime": 1.99,
    "text": "And I'm Mark Ruffalo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.0,
    "endTime": 6.106,
    "text": "And we're gonna take a BuzzFeed quiz to find out whether or not we would've survived the thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.106,
    "endTime": 7.54,
    "text": "Thanos's snap."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.54,
    "endTime": 9.6,
    "text": "Can you read a little slowly?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.6,
    "endTime": 10.2,
    "text": "I'll do my best."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.2,
    "endTime": 11.299999999999999,
    "text": "Okay, thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.3,
    "endTime": 13.898,
    "text": "(dramatic music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.4,
    "endTime": 20.5,
    "text": "Which Infinity Stone would you most like to get your hands on?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.5,
    "endTime": 21.0,
    "text": "Ooh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.0,
    "endTime": 22.3,
    "text": "Well, none of them, technically."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.3,
    "endTime": 24.3,
    "text": "But, what would I want to get my hands on?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.3,
    "endTime": 25.0,
    "text": "The reality, power?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.0,
    "endTime": 29.490000000000002,
    "text": "The options are reality, power, mind, time, soul, and space."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.49,
    "endTime": 30.2,
    "text": "I mean."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.2,
    "endTime": 31.18,
    "text": "I'm going mind."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.18,
    "endTime": 32.189,
    "text": "I'm going time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.189,
    "endTime": 35.69,
    "text": "Which Disney character would you choose to join the Avengers?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.69,
    "endTime": 36.57,
    "text": "I love this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.57,
    "endTime": 44.5,
    "text": "Queen Elsa, Hercules, Genie, Sorcerer Mickey, Elastigirl, or Stitch."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.5,
    "endTime": 46.0,
    "text": "- Gosh, that a tough one. - Ooh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 50.0,
    "text": "I mean there's function and then there's just personal preference."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.19,
    "endTime": 52.683,
    "text": "I'm gonna go from a same point of function, it's gotta be Genie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.683,
    "endTime": 53.3,
    "text": "I'm going to Genie too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.3,
    "endTime": 54.87,
    "text": "If you don't pick Genie, you're kind of an idiot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.87,
    "endTime": 56.37,
    "text": "Alright, I'm going to Genie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.3,
    "endTime": 61.65,
    "text": "Which word would your closest friends use to describe you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.65,
    "endTime": 63.33,
    "text": "Caring? Loyal?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.33,
    "endTime": 64.163,
    "text": "Yup."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.163,
    "endTime": 67.5,
    "text": "Creative? Funny? Kind? Successful?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.5,
    "endTime": 68.9,
    "text": "I'm kind of your friend."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.9,
    "endTime": 72.539,
    "text": "- I'm gonna say my-- - I'd say you're kind, and successful, and loyal, and creative."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.54,
    "endTime": 74.30000000000001,
    "text": "All of them, can I just click all of them?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.3,
    "endTime": 76.46,
    "text": "I think my buddies would say loyal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.46,
    "endTime": 78.0,
    "text": "That's what my buddies would say too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.0,
    "endTime": 78.7,
    "text": "Oh, sure they would, Mark."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.7,
    "endTime": 80.5,
    "text": "They would, I swear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.5,
    "endTime": 81.52,
    "text": "Typical Mark."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.52,
    "endTime": 84.92,
    "text": "Which is your favorite MCU dynamic duo?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.5,
    "endTime": 86.58,
    "text": "Hope and Scott?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.58,
    "endTime": 88.13,
    "text": "Thor and Loki?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.13,
    "endTime": 94.8,
    "text": "Steve and Bucky？The Science Bros？Gamora and Nebula？Carol and Fury？"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.8,
    "endTime": 96.55,
    "text": "Buddy, you look all--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.55,
    "endTime": 97.42,
    "text": "Good and young."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.42,
    "endTime": 99.19,
    "text": "Which one are you gonna go for?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.19,
    "endTime": 100.36,
    "text": "You can't vote for yourself, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.36,
    "endTime": 101.193,
    "text": "That's a rule."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.193,
    "endTime": 102.41,
    "text": "That would be lame, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.41,
    "endTime": 104.0,
    "text": "Carol and Fury?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.0,
    "endTime": 105.71,
    "text": "Imma go with the Science Bros."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.71,
    "endTime": 106.3,
    "text": "You are?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.3,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "Not just 'cause you're here, just because."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 109.55,
    "text": "I'm going with Steve and Bucky."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.55,
    "endTime": 110.383,
    "text": "Atta boy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.383,
    "endTime": 111.57,
    "text": "That's not why I did it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.57,
    "endTime": 116.33999999999999,
    "text": "Which weird or unconventional superpower would you want to possess?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.34,
    "endTime": 116.8,
    "text": "Alright."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.8,
    "endTime": 120.3,
    "text": "The power to instantaneously learn any language by only hearing it once?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.3,
    "endTime": 125.0,
    "text": "The power to change the nutritional value of any food to your will?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.0,
    "endTime": 125.833,
    "text": "That's mine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.833,
    "endTime": 126.5,
    "text": "(laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.5,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "You don't even need to see the rest."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.0,
    "endTime": 131.0,
    "text": "The power to remember anything you read and recall it instantly?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.0,
    "endTime": 136.65,
    "text": "The power to make any and all clothing items fit you perfectly, as if tailored?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.65,
    "endTime": 138.19,
    "text": "You pick that, you're an asshole."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.19,
    "endTime": 142.459,
    "text": "The power to transform into any animal you can think of, real or imaginary?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.46,
    "endTime": 144.34,
    "text": "You're making this tough, Buzzfeed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.34,
    "endTime": 150.5,
    "text": "The power to always know, with absolute certainty, when someone is lying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.5,
    "endTime": 153.3,
    "text": "If you need that, you have to reassess your life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.3,
    "endTime": 157.299,
    "text": "I'm gonna have to have the power to know, with absolute certainty, when someone is lying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.3,
    "endTime": 160.77,
    "text": "Well, that flies in the face of what I just mumbled under my breath."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.77,
    "endTime": 161.70000000000002,
    "text": "Okay, great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.7,
    "endTime": 166.22199999999998,
    "text": "The only thing that's making me the second guess, the power to transform into any animal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.223,
    "endTime": 167.0,
    "text": "Oh, to fly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.0,
    "endTime": 167.8,
    "text": "That's really good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.8,
    "endTime": 168.88500000000002,
    "text": "To fly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.885,
    "endTime": 170.37,
    "text": "It's really good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.37,
    "endTime": 171.0,
    "text": "I don't blame you if you go with that one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.0,
    "endTime": 174.32,
    "text": "The number one thing is to remember anything you read and recall it instantly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.32,
    "endTime": 175.78,
    "text": "How can you not?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.78,
    "endTime": 177.37,
    "text": "You still gotta deal with the idiots."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.37,
    "endTime": 178.5,
    "text": "I think I gotta go with the animal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.5,
    "endTime": 181.57,
    "text": "Now, remember the title of what this is about."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.57,
    "endTime": 183.29999999999998,
    "text": "It's surviving the snap."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.3,
    "endTime": 184.17100000000002,
    "text": "Wait a minute."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.171,
    "endTime": 184.7,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.7,
    "endTime": 186.29,
    "text": "I'm just doing this for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.29,
    "endTime": 188.334,
    "text": "Alright, then I'm still going to take the animal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.334,
    "endTime": 190.35,
    "text": "Okay, good, fair enough."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.35,
    "endTime": 194.1,
    "text": "Whose origin story is your personal favorite?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.1,
    "endTime": 194.6,
    "text": "I mean, I--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.6,
    "endTime": 196.4,
    "text": "Well, how does that have to do with the snap?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.4,
    "endTime": 201.94,
    "text": "Tony Stark, Steve Rogers, Thor, Stephen Strange, T'Challa, or Carol Danvers?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.94,
    "endTime": 204.5,
    "text": "- Where's-- - Origin story I'm gonna go with-- -"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.5,
    "endTime": 206.97,
    "text": "Wait, I'm missing mine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.97,
    "endTime": 212.35,
    "text": "Wait, there's--Tony Stark, Steve Rogers, Thor, Carol Danvers, T'Challa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.35,
    "endTime": 213.237,
    "text": "It's not there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.237,
    "endTime": 215.29999999999998,
    "text": "- I'm gonna go with-- - They put it on yours?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.3,
    "endTime": 216.579,
    "text": "No. (laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.58,
    "endTime": 218.11700000000002,
    "text": "- Look at Chris Hemsworth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.0,
    "endTime": 221.589,
    "text": "He had those dyed eyebrows."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.59,
    "endTime": 223.84,
    "text": "I'm gonna go with Steve Rogers, I mean, look at that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.84,
    "endTime": 224.81,
    "text": "Oh boy, tell you what."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.81,
    "endTime": 225.5,
    "text": "I love that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.5,
    "endTime": 228.2,
    "text": "- That was so freaking good. - If you were on there, I would vote for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.2,
    "endTime": 229.2,
    "text": "- Just so you know. - Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.2,
    "endTime": 230.13,
    "text": "I'm gonna go with Tony Stark."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.13,
    "endTime": 231.29999999999998,
    "text": "And finally--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.3,
    "endTime": 231.99,
    "text": "Oh, bummer, finally?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.99,
    "endTime": 233.43,
    "text": "I'm enjoying this, the best part of the day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.43,
    "endTime": 236.9,
    "text": "What would you say is your personal character flaw?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.9,
    "endTime": 237.84,
    "text": "Where's none?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.84,
    "endTime": 239.70000000000002,
    "text": "Now, wait, what does this have to do with the snap?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.7,
    "endTime": 240.76,
    "text": "We're gonna find out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.76,
    "endTime": 242.26,
    "text": "I joke around too much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.26,
    "endTime": 243.81,
    "text": "I have a short temper."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.81,
    "endTime": 245.27,
    "text": "I care too deeply."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.27,
    "endTime": 247.53,
    "text": "I'm too damn cool, too charming."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.53,
    "endTime": 249.22,
    "text": "I can be a little too blunt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.22,
    "endTime": 251.19,
    "text": "I'm always confident."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.19,
    "endTime": 253.737,
    "text": "I'm not always confident."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.737,
    "endTime": 255.656,
    "text": "The not is a big piece of that one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.656,
    "endTime": 257.5,
    "text": "- Oh, I'm sorry. I missed that. - I'm not always confident."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.5,
    "endTime": 259.4,
    "text": "I can be a little bit reckless."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.4,
    "endTime": 261.7,
    "text": "I would say you probably care too deeply."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.7,
    "endTime": 264.924,
    "text": "- I was gonna say that, but that's the most-- - Cliché."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.924,
    "endTime": 266.15,
    "text": "It's just really self-righteous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.15,
    "endTime": 268.29299999999995,
    "text": "- How could you care too deeply? - I'm too good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.293,
    "endTime": 270.1,
    "text": "How could you care too deeply?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.1,
    "endTime": 271.619,
    "text": "Well, that's better in the meantime."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.62,
    "endTime": 274.51,
    "text": "And the next one is I'm not always confident, but who the (beep) cares."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.51,
    "endTime": 275.409,
    "text": "I'm not too blunt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.41,
    "endTime": 276.41,
    "text": "You're a little reckless sometimes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.41,
    "endTime": 277.3,
    "text": "I have no temper."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.3,
    "endTime": 279.40000000000003,
    "text": "The reckless thing may be the thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.4,
    "endTime": 281.76,
    "text": "I have been in the car with you late at night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.76,
    "endTime": 283.46,
    "text": "You sure have, pal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.46,
    "endTime": 284.65,
    "text": "There it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.65,
    "endTime": 286.5,
    "text": "Maybe I can be a little reckless."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.5,
    "endTime": 288.271,
    "text": "I'm not always confident."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.271,
    "endTime": 289.86,
    "text": "(upbeat music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.86,
    "endTime": 290.88,
    "text": "Uh oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.88,
    "endTime": 291.777,
    "text": "You're not feeling so good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.777,
    "endTime": 292.3,
    "text": "Oh no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.3,
    "endTime": 295.7,
    "text": "I'm sorry, I didn't wanna tell you this, but you did not survive the Thanos snap!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.8,
    "endTime": 297.40000000000003,
    "text": "I don't know how I feel about this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.4,
    "endTime": 299.2,
    "text": "That sucks, man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.2,
    "endTime": 301.26,
    "text": "This is bull (beep), man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.26,
    "endTime": 302.60699999999997,
    "text": "I'm gonna tweet this out."
  }
]